# Project Nomenclature Guide

## General Naming Principles
1. Use descriptive, meaningful names that clearly indicate purpose.
2. Follow consistent casing conventions for each type of entity.
3. Avoid abbreviations unless widely understood.
4. Use domain-specific terminology from the supply chain industry.
5. Maintain consistency across all project components.

## Backend (Django) Naming Conventions

