- **Project Name**: `supply_chain` (snake_case)
- **Apps**: `users`, `orders`, `inventory`, `transportation`, `analytics`, `notifications` (snake_case)
- **Modules**: `ml`, `tasks`, `utils`, `services` (snake_case)

