## API Naming Conventions

### Endpoints
- **Base URL**: `/api/v1/` (kebab-case)
- **Resource Endpoints**: `/api/v1/users`, `/api/v1/orders`, `/api/v1/inventory` (kebab-case, plural)
- **Resource Detail**: `/api/v1/users/{id}`, `/api/v1/orders/{id}`, `/api/v1/inventory/{id}` (kebab-case)
- **Nested Resources**: `/api/v1/users/{id}/orders`, `/api/v1/orders/{id}/items` (kebab-case)
- **Action Endpoints**: `/api/v1/orders/{id}/process`, `/api/v1/inventory/{id}/adjust` (kebab-case)

### HTTP Methods
- **GET**: Retrieve resources.
- **POST**: Create resources.
- **PUT**: Update resources (full update).
- **PATCH**: Update resources (partial update).
- **DELETE**: Delete resources.

### Query Parameters
- **Filtering**: `?status=active`, `?category=electronics`, `?date_from=2023-01-01` (snake_case)
- **Sorting**: `?sort=created_at`, `?sort=-updated_at` (snake_case)
- **Pagination**: `?page=1`, `?limit=20` (snake_case)
- **Searching**: `?search=keyword`, `?q=query` (snake_case)

### Response Formats
- **Success**: `{ "data": [...], "meta": {...} }`
- **Error**: `{ "error": { "code": "...", "message": "..." } }`
- **Paginated**: `{ "data": [...], "meta": { "page": 1, "limit": 20, "total": 100 } }`

