## Git Naming Conventions

### Branches
- **Main Branches**: `main`, `develop`, `staging` (lowercase)
- **Feature Branches**: `feature/user-authentication`, `feature/order-management` (kebab-case)
- **Bugfix Branches**: `bugfix/login-error`, `bugfix/order-calculation` (kebab-case)
