- **Release Branches**: `release/v1.0.0`, `release/v2.0.0` (kebab-case)

### Commits
- **Commit Types**: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `style`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore` (lowercase)
- **Commit Format**: `type(scope): description` (lowercase)
- **Examples**:
